description: PM Mark Rutte no longer sees the blackface Christmas character as a harmless Netherlands tradition.
title: Dutch PM Rutte sceptical about Black Pete tradition
title_page: Dutch PM Rutte sceptical about Black Pete tradition - BBC News
maintext: The Freedom Party (PVV) leader went on: "We have a prime minister who now stands for nothing. The PVV holds on to national traditions well, for us Zwarte Piet will forever remain black!"
